snippet.textDisplay:
CONTAGIOUS COMPLAINING Numbers 11:10-15
I laugh at the serious joke that complaining is contagious. I read how Moses himself complained to GOD about the complaining people! Complaining to GOD is a serious sin. Complaining shows doubt, dissatisfaction, disrespect, and disdain. It says GOD’s provision isn’t enough, He can’t help us, He doesn’t know or care about our disposition, we don’t appreciate what He has and is doing, and that we need to find better alternatives (of which there are none). Stay away from complainers, don’t abide complaints, when you catch yourself complaining stop, remember your blessings and praise JESUS.
